          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "An elderly man crashed his Volkswagen Karmann Ghia in the city of Ballito on the afternoon of April 4. He hit a wall in the Long Island residential complex, the front end of the classic car sustaining significant damage. Even worse, the driver had to be transported to a local hospital.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
